title: Trapasso Pro II Tie Dye
description:
A day in the life through Nick Trapasso's eyes. The Converse CONS Trapasso Pro II sneakers now available in tie dye suede. Available at finer skate shops worldwide. 

Music courtesy of Wavy Heat by Library of Sands
